Rating: 2
I thought this dish was good, especially if you like dill with mustard, but I prefer more of a mayo/sour cream/pepper base with dill. As previous reviews suggested, I doubled the dressing recipe, but now I'm thinking maybe I shouldn't have! Perhaps it's because I don't like the combo of mustard and dill, but I thought the mustard flavor of the dressing was a little overpowering -- I couldn't even taste the chicken. Consequently, if I made this again, I would double the chicken, as other reviewers mentioned.

Rating: 4
